{"TopicId":173776,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Health mod?","CreatedByName":"Salticus","CreatedById":186923,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-11T17:09:25Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Salticus","CreatedById":186923,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-11T17:09:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:22px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E(Please ignore, I just dont know how to remove my posts) Health for Kerbals?\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, when i brushed my teeth yesterday, i had an idea: What about a mod wich adds health to your kerbals?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am no modder, but anyone could make this, if he would like to.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI thought about having health for your little green creatures, and if they crash into something they lose a bit of health. You can add first-aid-parts to your ship, and you can use them to restore health.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis could work great with life support mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf kerbals have got low health they get negative effects, I dont know wich, but it should be tweakable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf there is already a mod that does this please ignore this \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-04-12T12:55:02Z\u0022 title=\u002204/12/2018 12:55  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EApril 12, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Salticus\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JadeOfMaar","CreatedById":167617,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-11T20:22:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis mod fits the bill, but it does not account for kerbals bruising their knees and face. It works well alongside any life support mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed4816025312\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/155313-141-kerbal-health-112-2018-03-14/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Salticus","CreatedById":186923,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-12T12:55:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223351954\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173776\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221523478160\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167617\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JadeOfMaar\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, JadeOfMaar said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis mod fits the bill, but it does not account for kerbals bruising their knees and face. It works well alongside any life support mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed941775674\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/155313-141-kerbal-health-112-2018-03-14/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:212px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}